## Quality Gates

Run these checks in order before committing:
### Lint
- `go vet ./...`
- `golangci-lint run`

### Test
- `go test ./...`

### Ci (inferred from workflow)
- `go build -trimpath -ldflags="-w -s" -v`
- `go test -v -coverprofile="cover-profile.out" -short -race ./...`
- `go build -trimpath -o caddy-"$GOOS"-$GOARCH 2> /dev/null`
